<para>In the simplified information dialog,  you only get all the main information you should know about an element. The dialog covers three aspects of the element: <guilabel>General</guilabel>, <guilabel>States</guilabel> and
<guilabel>Energies</guilabel>.This dialog is available on right or left mouse click on an element, depending of your settings (default is right click).</para>

<screenshot>
<screeninfo>&kalzium;'s detailed information dialog</screeninfo>
<mediaobject>
<imageobject>
<imagedata fileref="screenshot4.png" format="PNG"/>
