<para>In the detailed information dialog,  you get a lot of information on an element. First an overview presents you the element, its symbol and atomic weight. The Miscellaneous tab tells you when it was discovered and its mean weight. The Picture tab displays a picture of the element when available. The Energies tab tells you about different energy facts related to the element. The Chemical Data tab presents some atomic data and the Atom Model tab displays the Atomix Hull</para>

</sect1>

