<sect1 id="colors">
<title>Color schemes</title>

<para>&kalzium; can show you which elements are where with regard to their Periodic <quote>block</quote> and <quote>group</quote>, their behavior with acid and which matter state (solid/liquid/vapor) they are in at a given temperature.</para>
